 URL => https://www.npmjs.com/package/json-server

 npm install -g json-server

 Create a products.json file with some data


 json-server --watch products.json  => this will server on default port 3000

json-server --watch products.json --port 8000 => this will server on  port 8000

Incase json-server is not working try with 
npx json-server --watch products.json --port 8000


Node.js - Runtime for Javascript
npm - Node package Manage